headline: 5 High ROE Stocks to Buy With Markets Likely to Wrap Up on a High
summary: DIS, LDOS, RJF, FTNT and HIG are some of the stocks with high ROE to profit from as investors await a "Santa Claus" rally to end the year on a high.
